{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act22side_level_act22side_03_end","storyGroup":"act22side","storySort":7,"storyDependence":"act22side_level_act22side_03_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"FC-3","storyName":"引燃草垛","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"众人在村庄过夜，安置伤员，风笛和苇草谈起了各自的过往。与此同时，阿赫茉妮意外听到了苇草纵火的消息，她瞬间的反应被菲舍尔捕捉到了。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act22side/level_act22side_03_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act22side_03","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":5,"next":7,"characters":["维恩","陈","莫兰","风笛","苇草","热情的商人","阿赫茉妮","菲舍尔","屏风后的女声","开斯特公爵"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e6/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutryinside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"唉，谁能想到逃难了这么多天，居然还能安安稳稳坐在屋子里吃上一顿热饭菜。","id":12,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"那个叫风笛的姑娘可真讨人喜欢，刚刚我们还在夸她炖的菜好吃呢。","id":13,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"嗯，这方面她确实不赖。","id":15,"figure":["avg_npc_662_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"安置的事，你们商量得顺利吗？","id":16,"figure":["avg_npc_662_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_725_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"都说定啦，赶不了路的人都可以留下，这两天先借两间仓库躲一躲。","id":18,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"逃难的人跟商队打了一架，又没真的抢到什么东西，这种事太常见了，办案的不会放在心上。","id":19,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"过个几天，广播里不报这些事情了，他们就不用躲了，可以动手建自己的房子了。","id":20,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"呃，不过得了矿石病的那几位，要住到离聚落远一些的地方去。","id":22,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"这里的人很友善。","id":24,"figure":["avg_npc_662_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"唉，是啊，我们当初逃出来的时候，一路上要是有人收留，也不至于变成现在这样。","id":26,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"可这也不怪别人。以前聚落里收留一两批逃难的人，不是难事，只是现在大家都过得越来越糟糕了。","id":27,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"你瞧塞尔蒙那小孩，要是有个地方能容下他们兄妹俩，她也不至于一直在各个聚落之间窜来窜去，到处惹事。","id":28,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"像咱们今天晚上可以在村子里过夜，但塞尔蒙坚持自己在村外躲着，就是因为她在这里抢过人家的牧兽，现在不好意思见那位老爷子......","id":30,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......唉，当我没说。让她听到了，又要说我不尊重她。","id":31,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",5]},{"type":"dialog","id":32},{"type":"character","id":33},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":34},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":35},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":36},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":37},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":38},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":39},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"晚上好......","id":41,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#4$1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"啊，莫兰？天都黑了，你怎么过来的？趁现在还有灯，我带你回去......","id":43,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"谢谢，但我已经习惯摸黑走路了......","id":45,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"......请问，苇草在吗？","id":47,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#1$1","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你找她？她独自出门了。","id":49,"figure":["avg_npc_662_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"也许苇草是有什么烦心事吧......自从来了这里，塞尔蒙就不肯和她说话。","id":51,"figure":["avg_npc_725_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_662_1#8$1","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"别担心，风笛去找她了。","id":53,"figure":["avg_npc_662_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"嗯......或者换个说法，我们不如担心苇草会嫌太吵吧。","id":54,"figure":["avg_npc_662_1",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":55},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":56},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":57},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":58},{"type":"character","id":59},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_bg_34_g4_swamp_n.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":60},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":61},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_normal_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":62,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":63},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":64},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#2","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1","focus":"-1","id":65},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","text":"","id":66},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":67},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"50","fadetime":"0.6","isblock":"true","id":68},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":69},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"50","fadetime":"0.3","block":"false","id":70},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-20","fadetime":"0.4","block":"false","id":71},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":72},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown3","volume":"1","id":73},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":74},{"type":"jump","name":"left","xpos":"-100","power":"10","times":"1","fadetime":"0.5","block":"false","id":75},{"type":"jump","name":"right","xpos":"20","power":"5","times":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":76},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":77},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#2","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1","focus":"1","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"哇，抱歉！","id":79,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#2","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1","focus":"2","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......没事。","id":81,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#3","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1","focus":"1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"欸，我没想到这里会有人，没太仔细看。每次钟声一响，周围就黑黢黢的，眼睛要过一会儿才能习惯。","id":83,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"还好撞上的是你，换成其他人，可能就要被我撞倒了。","id":84,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1","focus":"1","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"不过，我记得大家说好今天晚上不用放哨？","id":86,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我只是......想在外面坐坐。","id":88,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#8","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"啊，干草的味道很好闻，对吧。","id":90,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#8","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......干草？","id":92,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#8","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"是呀，那边的干草垛。我好久没闻到过这种气味了，所以跑出来好好地闻一闻。","id":94,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"以前我准备考军校的时候，读理论知识读得头疼了，只要在干草垛上面躺一会儿，就感觉什么都好了。","id":95,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"虽然妈妈总说我这是在偷懒，不能因为想问题太辛苦就不去想......可是脑子里有太多东西的话，就是挺累人的呀。","id":96,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#8","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......嗯。","id":98,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#8","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"所以，把手给我一下？","id":100,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#8","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"呃......","id":102,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#9","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"来来来，一起躺嘛！就一会儿！","id":104,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"虽然我不擅长想事情，也许帮不了你什么，但干草垛肯定能帮上你的！","id":105,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",8]},{"type":"dialog","id":106},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":107},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":108},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.6","id":109},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_hidehaystack","volume":"0.9","delay":"0.2","id":110},{"type":"image","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2.5","block":"true","id":111},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"嘿——！","id":113},{"type":"dialog","id":114},{"type":"character","id":115},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":116},{"type":"text","text":"风笛放松地躺在草垛上，轻轻哼着刚才从农户那里学来的歌谣。","id":117},{"type":"text","text":"一阵温润的夜风吹过，苇草按照她的建议，深深地吸了一口气。","id":118},{"type":"text","text":"但她闻到的不是干草的香气，而是潮湿的泥土与灰尘的味道。","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"想到自己竟然三年多没有回过家了，总觉得好奇怪呀。","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"你想呀，地等着我去翻土，麦子等着我去收割......一年不回家，就会把所有重要的事情全部错过一遍。","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"就连家里寄来的信，我也要等下一次回罗德岛的时候才能收到。","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"你......很想家吗？","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"当然啦。你呢？你是小丘郡人吗？","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......不是。","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"但我以前也生活在和小丘郡差不多的城市里......深红色的砖墙，灰色的人行道，两三层高的房子，花藤会长到窗户外面。","id":126},{"type":"dialog","id":127},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我......很怀念那段平静的时光。","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"那个时候，家里放着很多旧书，有的还是手抄本。我总是躲到书房里，锁上门，那样就不用听别人讲话。","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"啊，你家里人很多所以太吵了？还是经常有人做客？","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......不，还好。只是躲起来就可以避免很多麻烦。","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"从书房的窗户，可以看到街道，看到父母结束一天的工作归来。","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"如果可以的话，我很想回到那里。","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"啊，难道你说的地方已经......","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯。","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"抱歉......我是不是让你更难过了？","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"没关系的，那是很早以前的事情了。","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我和小丘郡那些生活被毁掉的普通人，或者眼前这些背井离乡的流民，也许没有太大差别。","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"大家可以在这里安顿下来，重新搭起房子......可是，他们的家乡在哪里呢？","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"还有那些，不得不走得更远的人......他们又要逃到哪里去呢？","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"唔......这些问题光靠一个人想是想不出答案的吧？","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯......","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"但我也不是说你想这些就没用啦！","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"一个人想不出答案的话，我们可以一起想。以前我遇到做不出的题的时候，就老去骚扰陈陈。","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"后来，我就总是拉着队长......她们嘴上嫌我烦，可每一次都会陪我聊天，帮我解决难题的。","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"你呢，你有什么能说心里话的人吗？比如姐妹啊同学啊战友啊之类......","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":148},{"type":"dialog","id":149},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我有......姐姐。","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"但是......","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"你们关系不太好吗？","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......不，我不该这么说。我不该......","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"其实塞尔蒙有一点说得对，你总是习惯性地说“不”。","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"但是她有一点弄错了，你呀，在说到自己的事的时候，才最喜欢说“不”，就好像......唔，我说不上来，就好像要费劲摆脱什么似的。","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......有人对我说过类似的话。","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"欸欸，是吗？","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"她......救了我，对我说，我不需要寻求死亡，也可以挣脱原本的命运。","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"Outcast呀，这确实很像她的语气。","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我很后悔......后悔自己没能努力再和她多说几句话。","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我很想问问她，为什么要救我？","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"她......从我身上看到了什么？","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"唉，我也不确定她会怎样回答。","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"不过苇草，在问她之前，你有问过自己吗？你从你自己身上看到了什么？","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我......自己？","id":166},{"type":"dialog","id":167},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":168},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":169},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_hidehaystack","volume":"0.9","id":170},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.6","delay":"2","id":171},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":172},{"type":"image","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":173},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":174},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"啊，那边有人出来了。","id":176,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"那个摸索的动作，应该是莫兰......她夜里看不见。","id":178,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#2","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"哇，那她怎么自己跑出来了。","id":180,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"莫兰小姐！有什么我们能帮忙的吗？","id":182,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"啊，你先站在那里等一下，我们过来啦。","id":183,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":184},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":185},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":186},{"type":"character","id":187},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_bg_34_g4_swamp_n.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":188},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":189},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":191},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"......谢谢。","id":193,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"请问，苇草在哪里？他们说，她出门了。","id":195,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":196},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":197},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我就在这里。","id":200,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"......抱歉。请问，我可以跟你们一起走吗？","id":202,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"去哪里都行。我还有些力气，能干活......也能战斗。","id":203,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":205,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"你想......战斗？","id":206,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"嗯。他们都说我活不久了，只能在哪个角落里悄无声息地死去。","id":208,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"可我不想这样。","id":209,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"“如果你作为塔拉人还想活下去，那就换车间，接受更低的工资”“如果你得了矿石病还想活下去，那就从这搬走，去感染者街区”......","id":211,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"我不想再听这种话了。","id":212,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"苇草，我以前不会这样想，但我遇见了你。","id":214,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"他们告诉我，你也是感染者。是你说服了塞尔蒙和其他人，带着我们走到了这里。","id":215,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"你......也和维恩一样，相信我？","id":217,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"请不要有压力，我......我不想拖累你，拖累任何人。","id":219,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"我只是想做点什么，做什么都好。像我这样的人，已经不会再失去什么了。","id":220,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"要是我能为其他塔拉人带去一点什么的话，我想去做。要是我的腿还能往前走的话，我想和你们一起走。","id":221,"figure":["avg_npc_728_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":223,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#8","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"我觉得可以欸。苇草，不管怎么样，我们先一起走吧，好不好？","id":225,"figure":["avg_222_bpipe_1",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":226},{"type":"character","id":227},{"type":"text","text":"对红发瓦伊凡而言，这可能并不是一个需要苇草回答的问题。因为得到答案之前，她已经开始拉着苇草往前走了。","id":228},{"type":"text","text":"苇草回头看了眼另一个人。她知道，莫兰有夜盲症，到了晚上需要别人引路。","id":229},{"type":"text","text":"没有什么犹豫的时间，苇草向莫兰伸出了手。","id":230},{"type":"dialog","id":231},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......一起走吧。","id":233,"figure":["avg_1020_reed2_1",8]},{"type":"dialog","id":234},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":236},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":237},{"type":"character","id":238},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5b/Avg_bg_34_g5_noblehall.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":239},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":240},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":241,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":242},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":243},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"阿赫茉妮小姐，您可算来啦。我还以为今天没机会见到您呢。","id":245,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"既然是子爵大人举办的酒会，我又怎么可能错过？","id":247,"figure":["avg_npc_228_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"当然，当然。您可是特伦特侯爵的朋友，子爵大人的贵客。","id":249,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"多亏了您介绍，我先前那单生意才能做成。我可一直想找机会谢谢您。","id":250,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"不必那么客气，霍尔先生。","id":252,"figure":["avg_npc_228_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"我既没有贵族身份，名下也没什么产业，充其量只是个替大人物们奔走的信使罢了。","id":253,"figure":["avg_npc_228_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":254},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":255},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":256},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"（举杯）","id":258,"figure":["avg_4017_puzzle_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":259},{"type":"dialog","id":260},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":261},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":262},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"那位是......","id":264,"figure":["avg_npc_228_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"市政部门的红人，菲舍尔先生。","id":266,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"哦？先前我可没怎么听说过他呢。","id":268,"figure":["avg_npc_228_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"菲舍尔先生调到这个郡也就是前不久的事情。像他这样的年轻人，想要取得快速升迁的机会，总要格外努力一些。","id":270,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"呵呵，谁又不是呢？","id":272,"figure":["avg_npc_228_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"您过谦了。","id":274,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"对了，我听几位朋友说，最近大公爵们的军队调动都很频繁，各大公爵领的核心城市均已戒严。","id":275,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"您的消息一向灵通......能否透露一下，战争是不是近在眼前？","id":276,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"报纸上都是这么预测的吧？毕竟，公爵们的舰队早就抵达伦蒂尼姆的城墙外啦。","id":278,"figure":["avg_npc_228_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"我并不是很关心萨卡兹，我是指大公爵之间......咳，我听说，只是听说而已。","id":280,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"最近有许多源石燃料流向特伦特郡。侯爵大人与开斯特公爵向来交好，可是特伦特郡与铁公爵的领地毗邻......","id":281,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"哎呀，霍尔先生，跨城燃料交易可是必须经过审批的。想必您在市政部门一定有非常好的朋友，对吧？","id":283,"figure":["avg_npc_228_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"哈......哈哈，都是为了生意而已。","id":285,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"阿赫茉妮小姐，虽说您对战争的事情没那么感兴趣，但是......您是从其他城市赶来的，对吧？","id":286,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"幸好，您来时没有遇到什么麻烦，但返程时，还请继续小心。","id":287,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"我听说，移动城市外面的聚落很乱，时不时有叛乱分子出没，前几天还有人纵火。","id":288,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"什么样的叛乱分子值得您的关注？","id":290,"figure":["avg_npc_228_1",6]},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":291},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"说不上关注，类似的事件在那些乡巴佬出没的地方可多得是。","id":293,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"奇怪的是那火......哈哈，也未必是真的，就当个乡野奇闻说给您听听吧。","id":294,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"据目击者说，那火和一般的火都不太一样，威力跟爆炸似的，现场却找不到源石爆炸物的痕迹，又极难扑灭......","id":295,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialog","id":296},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"200","g":"200","b":"200","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_plot_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":299,"musicid":3},{"type":"background","id":300},{"type":"character","id":301},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":302},{"type":"image","screenadapt":"coverall","id":303},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"-30","yFrom":"10","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.05","yScaleFrom":"1.05","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"6","block":"false","id":304},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"200","g":"200","b":"200","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":305},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"......","id":307},{"type":"dialog","id":308},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":309},{"type":"text","text":"特别的火。","id":310},{"type":"text","text":"虽然很可能只是巧合，但类似的形容她很熟悉。","id":311},{"type":"text","text":"难道是......拉芙希妮？","id":312},{"type":"text","text":"阿赫茉妮很惊讶。","id":313},{"type":"text","text":"“校官”的提醒的确唤醒了她心底的些许忧虑。自从那艘名为罗德岛的舰船驶入维多利亚，她有一阵没能得到关于拉芙希妮的消息了。","id":314},{"type":"text","text":"毫无疑问，一定有人在帮罗德岛隐匿行踪，这家医药公司显然比她最初设想的还要不简单。","id":315},{"type":"text","text":"而这也意味着，身在罗德岛的拉芙希妮并不会轻易地被维多利亚的其他势力找到。","id":316},{"type":"text","text":"可是为什么......为什么拉芙希妮会离开那艘船？","id":317},{"type":"text","text":"为什么她会出现在距离爱布拉娜这么近的地方？","id":318},{"type":"image","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":319},{"type":"text","text":"在阿赫茉妮身后，一道视线投向了她。","id":320},{"type":"text","text":"从阿赫茉妮踏入这个宴会厅开始，她的一举一动自然都被关注着。","id":321},{"type":"text","text":"可直到这一刻，那道视线才真正聚焦在了她身上。","id":322},{"type":"dialog","id":323},{"type":"dialog","id":324},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":326},{"type":"image","id":327},{"type":"character","id":328},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5b/Avg_bg_34_g5_noblehall.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":329},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":330},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":331},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":332},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的商人","text":"阿赫茉妮小姐？","id":334,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"......嗯？","id":336,"figure":["avg_npc_228_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#1","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"抱歉......我刚刚在想晚上舞会的事。您觉得我佩戴什么颜色的耳饰比较好？","id":338,"figure":["avg_npc_228_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":339},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":340},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":341},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":342},{"type":"character","id":343},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":344},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":345},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":346,"musicid":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":347},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":348},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"......先生，您应当看过相关卷宗，还有我所有的报告了。","id":350,"figure":["avg_4017_puzzle_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"我建议我们立刻开始行动......","id":351,"figure":["avg_4017_puzzle_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"屏风后的女声","text":"做得很好，年轻人。你品尝过长桌上的威士忌夹心巧克力了吗？","id":353,"figure":["avg_4017_puzzle_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"——！","id":355,"figure":["avg_4017_puzzle_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"......贵安，开斯特公爵阁下。我没有想到您会光临这场宴会，还特意在这里等待。","id":356,"figure":["avg_4017_puzzle_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":357},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":358},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":359},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":360},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"谁能错过这场盛大的宴会呢？仅仅是在隔间里听着室内乐队的演奏，就令人心旷神怡。","id":362,"figure":["avg_npc_726_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"真希望你也同样享受。","id":363,"figure":["avg_npc_726_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"我......还有任务在身，不容松懈。","id":365,"figure":["avg_4017_puzzle_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_726_1#7$1","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"我们所做的一切努力，终究是为了众人能享受宁静的生活。","id":367,"figure":["avg_npc_726_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"情报人员虽然作为瞭望者，不得不在和平的年代里也保持神经紧绷，但总会有获得宁静的那一天。","id":368,"figure":["avg_npc_726_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"对了，你的身体状况如何？","id":370,"figure":["avg_npc_726_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"......承蒙公爵阁下关照。您竟然关注到了我这样一名普通情报人员的感染状况。","id":372,"figure":["avg_4017_puzzle_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"我——","id":373,"figure":["avg_4017_puzzle_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"不用紧张，你没有隐瞒什么。如我所言，你做得很好。","id":375,"figure":["avg_npc_726_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"这次任务结束后，作为奖赏，你是想要擢升，还是想要退出呢？","id":376,"figure":["avg_npc_726_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":377},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":378},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":379},{"type":"character","id":380},{"type":"image","id":381}],"characters":["维恩","陈","莫兰","风笛","苇草","热情的商人","阿赫茉妮","菲舍尔","屏风后的女声","开斯特公爵"]}